track_notes: No much walk for this 2 summits, but one of them has no really good track, you must go throught small trees and this is a bit ennoying.
This summit as no interest! at the end of the ascent it is difficult to walk in between small trees. try to go on the left handside to found the best passage.
you can use this path if the dechetterie is open, neverless it is not a realy nice summit
